<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF956A2AFA4F934019F2BEB8" pageId="110" pageNumber="868" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF956A2AFA4F934019F2BEB8" blockId="110.[1456,2663,871,1536]" pageId="110" pageNumber="868">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF956A2AFA4F93401911BE08" bold="true" box="[1459,1809,1305,1338]" pageId="110" pageNumber="868">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. Mainly found in pristine forests, which are being destroyed. Habitat loss, together with limited range, makes the species very vulnerable.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
